channel.description:
In my time of coding, I've NEVER once had this problem. [code]Compiling net/com/codeusa/*.java .
et\com\codeusa
et\packethandler\ActionButtons.java:1564: variable playerMagi c might not have been initialized playerMagic.updateAttributes(p.autocastSpellbook, p.autocastSpel l); ^ .
et\com\codeusa
et\packethandler\ActionButtons.java:1588: variable playerMagi c might not have been initialized playerMagic.updateAttributes(p.autocastSpellbook, p.autocastSpel l); ^ 2 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code] By the way, it's z508.
